  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to evaluate the efficacy, safety, and tolerability of
      cariprazine monotherapy versus placebo for the treatment of acute manic or mixed episodes
      associated with bipolar I disorder.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
